This paper is primarily focused on image feature matching, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel optimization framework that involves game theory and clustering, which could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses geometric compatibility, which could be categorized under graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper mentions applications in robotics (cs.RO), which could also be a relevant sub-category.
